snippet.title: Yupitergrad 2: The Lost Station - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Yupitergrad 2: The Lost Station has landed - bigger and stronger. Explore a space station full of rogue machines, use new gadgets, free your companion AIsha and experience an epic adventure in this full-scale metroidvania for VR.

▶️▶️▶️

The game is now available on Pico Neo 3 and Pico 4 headests, and will be released on Meta Quest 2, Steam and HTC Elite XR. Stay tuned for more dates on our social media channels:
